[30;1m55 | [0m[35m    - The `ex` parameter represents the expiration time in seconds.[0m
[30;1m56 | [0m[35m    - The `px` parameter represents the expiration time in milliseconds.[0m
[30;1m57 | [0m[35m    - The `nx` parameter, if True, sets the value only if the key does not exist.[0m
